summary:
Passionate, persistent, and getting things done. Focused on delivery, quality, and detail. Outspoken, ethical, accountable, and with a good sense of humour. 

I spent the last few years focusing on my family, an instinct based decision which in retrospective turned to be the most rewarding on all possible levels. 
Having accomplished that I am excited and ready to return to work. I am equally open to almost all types of humanitarian volunteering work, including experiences abroad.
